### Contoh request API WAHA (pakai VS Code extension "REST Client")
### Sesuaikan @baseUrl dan @apiKey dengan environment Anda.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@apiKey = GANTI_DENGAN_WAHA_API_KEY
@session = default

### Cek status server
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/server/status
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Mulai session WhatsApp
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/sessions/{{session}}/start
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Cek status session (scan QR via dashboard jika status SCAN_QR_CODE)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/sessions/{{session}}
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Ambil QR code untuk login
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/{{session}}/auth/qr
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Kirim pesan teks
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/sendText
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "session": "{{session}}",
  "chatId": "6281234567890@c.us",
  "text": "Halo dari WAHA! 👋"
}

### Stop session
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/sessions/{{session}}/stop
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}
